{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Make an agreed offer on a property legally binding",
        "additional_details": "When buyers withdraw from property sales without warning, it can cost people money.",
        "background": "I want the government to legislate to change the point at which there is a binding contract during house sales. Once an offer has been agreed, I think here should be a financial penalty for pulling out of the contract.",
